### Broken Assumptions (Evidence-Based)

1. **Role dashboards have no backend** — [StudentDashboard.tsx](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20new%20updae%202.0/frontend/src/pages/student/StudentDashboard.tsx), [TeacherDashboard.tsx](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20new%20updae%202.0/frontend/src/pages/teacher/TeacherDashboard.tsx), [EmployeeDashboard.tsx](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20new%20updae%202.0/frontend/src/pages/employee/EmployeeDashboard.tsx) exist but NO corresponding APIs. Status: `[FAKE]`

2. **Attendance endpoint is a stub** — Line 579-592 in [index.php](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20new%20updae%202.0/api/index.php):
   ```php
   // This is a placeholder - full implementation would go here
   $response->getBody()->write(json_encode(['success' => true, 'message' => 'Attendance marked successfully']));
   ```
   Never touches `gibbonAttendanceLogPerson`. Status: `[BROKEN]`

3. **Timetable endpoint is a stub** — Line 617-627 in [index.php](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20new%20updae%202.0/api/index.php):
   ```php
   // This is a placeholder - full implementation would go here
   ```
   Never queries `gibbonTT*` tables. Status: `[BROKEN]`

4. **Courses pages are static** — [Courses.tsx](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20new%20updae%202.0/frontend/src/pages/Courses.tsx) and [CourseDetail.tsx](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20new%20updae%202.0/frontend/src/pages/CourseDetail.tsx) exist, but NO API. `gibbonCourse` table exists but unused. Status: `[FAKE]`

5. **No RBAC enforcement on most endpoints** — Only `authMiddleware` checks JWT validity. No role-based access control except `PermissionManager::requirePermission` on 2 endpoints. Any authenticated user can access `/admin/*`.

### Root Cause Summary

1. **UI-first development** — Pages built before backend, never connected
2. **Stub APIs left in place** — Placeholder responses return fake success
3. **No role middleware** — JWT decoded but role never enforced
4. **Gibbon tables underutilized** — Full ERP schema exists, queries not written
5. **No API contracts** — Frontend expects data that backend doesn't provide

