## 6. EXECUTION PLAN

### Phase 1: Fix Critical RBAC (3h)

```
[x] 1.1 Create RoleMiddleware.php (1h)
    - Extract role from JWT
    - 403 if unauthorized
    
[ ] 1.2 Apply to all /admin/* routes (1h)
    - Add ->add(requireRole(['admin']))
    
[ ] 1.3 Test role enforcement (1h)
    - Login as student, try /admin/users → 403
```

### Phase 2: Fix Attendance API (4h)

```
[ ] 2.1 Implement POST /attendance/mark (2h)
    - Insert into gibbonAttendanceLogPerson
    - Validate class ownership for teachers
    
[ ] 2.2 Implement GET /attendance (1h)
    - Query by class_id + date
    - Return student list with status
    
[ ] 2.3 Connect AttendanceManagement.tsx (1h)
    - Replace mock data with API calls
```

### Phase 3: Build Role Dashboards (6h)

```
[ ] 3.1 Student Dashboard API (2h)
    - GET /student/dashboard
    - Profile, attendance summary, notifications
    
[ ] 3.2 Teacher Dashboard API (2h)
    - GET /teacher/dashboard
    - Classes, today's schedule, attendance counts
    
[ ] 3.3 Connect dashboard UIs (2h)
```

### Phase 4: Delete Fake Features (1h)

```
[ ] 4.1 Remove or mark as "Coming Soon":
    - ManageContent.tsx (no backend)
    - Team.tsx, FacultyDetail.tsx (no API)
    - Courses.tsx hardcoded data OR build API
```

### Phase 5: Add Frontend Route Guards (2h)

```
[ ] 5.1 Create ProtectedRoute.tsx
    - Check localStorage role
    - Redirect if unauthorized
    
[ ] 5.2 Wrap all /admin/* routes
[ ] 5.3 Wrap role-specific routes
```

### Phase 6: Refactor Backend (4h, Optional)

```
